OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1771920251
OL,3,CLovejoy episode helps antiques dealer
OL,4,Cspot plaques stolen from Napoleon III
OL,5,Ctomb
OL,7,FTwo of three "priceless" altar plaques
OL,8,Fstolen from the crypt of Napoleon
OL,9,FBonaparte III in a Hampshire monastery
OL,10,Fhave been recovered after an antiques
OL,11,Fdealer recognised identifying marks
OL,12,Ffrom a 30-year-old episode of Lovejoy.
OL,14,FThe wooden prayer frames, which date
OL,15,Fback to the 19th century, were taken
OL,16,Fin a burglary at St Michael's Abbey in
OL,17,FFarnborough in February 2014.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
