PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1771920251
OL,3,CLovejoy episode helps antiques dealer
OL,4,Cspot plaques stolen from Napoleon III
OL,5,Ctomb
OL,7,FNapoleon III, the nephew of Napoleon
OL,8,FBonaparte, fled in exile to England in
OL,9,F1871 after losing the Franco-Prussian
OL,10,Fwar and being captured by the Germans.
OL,12,FHe died in 1873 after surgery for
OL,13,Fbladder stones.
OL,15,FIn 1880, his widow, Empress Eugenie,
OL,16,Fbought a house in Farnborough and
OL,17,Fbuilt St Michael's Abbey as a
OL,18,Fmonastery with the Imperial Mausoleum
OL,19,Ffor the remains of her husband and her
OL,20,Fson, Napoleon, who died in the Zulu
OL,21,FWar in 1879.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
