OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1771920251
OL,3,CLovejoy episode helps antiques dealer
OL,4,Cspot plaques stolen from Napoleon III
OL,5,Ctomb
OL,7,FWhen his body was retrieved from the
OL,8,Fbattlefield, a number of handwritten
OL,9,Fprayers were found in his wallet which
OL,10,FEugenie had engraved and mounted to
OL,11,Fform the prayer frames which were
OL,12,Fstolen in the burglary.
OL,14,FIn 2023, Roger Karoutchi, deputy
OL,15,Fspeaker of the French senate, called
OL,16,Ffor the remains of Napoleon III to be
OL,17,Freturned to France, saying that he was
OL,18,Fthe only sovereign who was buried
OL,19,Fabroad.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
